  Copyright (c) 2016-present, Facebook Inc.

- **PyTorch Geometric** - MIT License
  Copyright (c) 2021 Matthias Fey

- **Transformers (HuggingFace)** - Apache License 2.0
  Copyright 2018- The Hugging Face team

- **BioBERT** - Apache License 2.0
  Copyright 2019 DMIS Lab, Korea University

- **NumPy** - BSD License
  Copyright (c) 2005-2023, NumPy Developers

- **Pandas** - BSD 3-Clause License
  Copyright (c) 2008-2023, AQR Capital Management, LLC

### Data Sources

The project integrates publicly available biomedical databases:

- **STRING Database** - Creative Commons BY 4.0
  Szklarczyk et al., Nucleic Acids Research (2023)
  https://string-db.org/

- **BioGRID** - MIT License
  Oughtred et al., Nucleic Acids Research (2021)
  https://thebiogrid.org/

- **DisGeNET** - ODbL 1.0 License (Open Database License)
  Piñero et al., Nucleic Acids Research (2020)
  https://www.disgenet.org/

- **Human Phenotype Ontology (HPO)** - Custom License (Free for research)
  Köhler et al., Nucleic Acids Research (2021)
  https://hpo.jax.org/

- **Orphanet** - Creative Commons BY 4.0
  INSERM, Orphanet
  https://www.orphadata.com/

### Pretrained Models

- **BioBERT** - Apache License 2.0
  Lee et al., Bioinformatics (2020)
  https://github.com/dmis-lab/biobert

- **PubMedBERT** - Apache License 2.0
  Gu et al., AAAI (2021)
  https://huggingface.co/microsoft/BiomedNLP-PubMedBERT

